title: Man Tries To ‘Squirrel Proof’ Bird Feeder, But The Determined Rodent Has Other Ideas
text:
Man Tries To ‘Squirrel Proof’ Bird Feeder, But The Determined Rodent Has Other Ideas   
Squirrels will do just about anything they can to get to some yummy food! This squirrel encounters a “squirrel proofed” bird feeder, but he’s not about to let a human’s contraption get in the way of a tasty snack. 
Share this cute video with your friends and family.
